{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_01_03",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 3話 お花と猫と写真",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市の情報誌から、地元出身アイドルを紹介する）\n（グラビアページの依頼がきた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(A Hoshimi City magazine has made a job offer)\n(for some gravure work introducing local idols.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.964101541042328,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はこういう仕事はまだやったことがなかったよな\nせっかくの機会だし、出てみないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei hadn't done this kind of work yet‚ right?\nThis seems like a good opportunity. Want to give it a try?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.60668392414,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、いいよー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ okay.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.404603290557862,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そうか、良かった\n芽衣もアイドルとしてどんどん露出を増やしていこう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Really? Great.\nA great chance to get you more exposure as an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.34609405323863,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "でも、仕事の詳細次第かな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it depends on the details of the job.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.786734747886666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣のセクシーな水着姿を初披露するんでしょ？\n簡単には出れないなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do I have to wear sexy swimwear for the first time?\nI’m not sure I’m ready for that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.49712397903204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "違う違う！\n水着は着なくていい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no!\nNo need to wear swimwear.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.761215053285895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "な～んだ、そうなんだ\nどんな撮影なの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What? There isn’t?\nSo what’s the job?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "屋外で衣装を着て\n猫と遊ぶアイドルの写真を撮るそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’ll be wearing outfits outside\nand taking some pics with cats.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "猫！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Cats?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.71374170780185,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣、猫大好き！　どんな子が来るのかな？\nアメショーにペルシャ……楽しみだなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love cats! What kind of cats?\nAmerican shorthair? Persian? Oh‚ I can’t wait!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.563333563009934,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "さ、さあ……\n一応事前に聞いてみるよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve… no idea.\nI guess I can ask.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.666666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、楽しみだな～\nいっぱい遊ぼ～っと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. I’m so excited!\nFun with cats!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.43861705859507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "（こうして芽衣と一緒に猫と遊びに）\n（……ではなく、グラビア撮影に行くことになった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Mei agrees to go play with the cats—)\n(that is‚ take part in the gravure work.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.72195039192839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10266.666666666666,
          "startTime": 78.98861705859505
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "カメラマン",
      "speakerNameEn": "Photographer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はい、次は猫を抱き上げて笑顔下さーい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay! Lift up the next cat and give a smile!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.15528372526174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "うふふ、この子可愛い～\nあっこっちの子も！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe. Such a cutie.\nOh‚ and this one too!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.53333333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 79.63537434339526
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "みんなまとめて連れて帰りたいくらいだよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I just want to take them all home!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4294798413913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "カメラマン",
      "speakerNameEn": "Photographer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "いいね、いいね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good‚ that’s good!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.24378824631378,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 88.24378824631378
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1479.9999999999898,
          "startTime": 89.72378824631377
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_camera-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1680.0000000000068,
          "startTime": 89.92378824631379
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "カメラマン",
      "speakerNameEn": "Photographer",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その自然な笑顔、実に素晴らしい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Such a natural smile! Wonderful!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.76666666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cat-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3643.7971981366954,
          "startTime": 94.41046386480336
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "猫ちゃん、肉球ぷにぷに～\nあはは、可愛過ぎる～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What soft paws you have‚ kitty!\nHahaha. So cute!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.67713053147004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "お花はキレイだし、猫は可愛いし\n芽衣、すっごく楽しい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The flowers are lovely‚ and the cats are so cute.\nThis is so much fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "こんなお仕事ばっかだったらいいのにな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wish all my jobs were like this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.94605899994748,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "（最初はどうなるかと思ったけど、うまく行きそうだな）\n（芽衣の雰囲気も先方のイメージ通りみたいだし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I wondered what would happen‚ but this is going well.)\n(Mei is exactly who the client was looking for.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.52195690013468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.80240819797098
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.10240819797093
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、{user}さんも\nこっちにおいでよー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Say‚ {user}-san!\nCome over here and join me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.83574153130434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "猫、可愛いよー！　一緒に写真撮ろう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The cats are so cute! Let’s take a few shots together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.52675627812924,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 128.03369497403685
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いや、俺の写真はいらないから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ they don’t need any photos of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.03369497403685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.10095118627135
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "もう、そんなこと言わずにさ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don’t be like that!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.10095118627137,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくなんだから\nプロのカメラマンさんに撮ってもらおうよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You don’t get this opportunity every day.\nHave a professional take your picture!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.15858436425884,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_01_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "カメラマンさーん、ダメですか？",
      "translations": {
